data.text:
About Aralaguppe

Aralaguppe is a village in Chikmagalur tehsil in district of Chikmagalur, Karnataka, India. As per the data provided by Census of India in 2011, total population of Aralaguppe was 2,538 which includes 1,253 males and 1,285 females. Aralaguppe covers 1184.18 ha area. Pincode of Aralaguppe is 577131.
